1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 26]

14
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:48,840
I only wish for the safety
health and longevity of my family

15
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:51,670
without disasters or hardships.

16
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:54,800
I wish that Su Wan'er
and I will be together

17
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,270
for lifetimes,

18
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:57,470
never to be separated.

19
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:02,470
What if Bodhisattva let me

20
00:01:02,510 --> 00:01:04,670
reincarnate as a man in my next life?

21
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,590
Then I'll ask Bodhisattva

22
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,510
to let me be reborn as a woman.

23
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:10,720
I will marry you as your wife.

24
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:12,640
But what if we're born in

25
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,110
different places

26
00:01:14,230 --> 00:01:15,640
in the next life,

27
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,510
never to meet again?

28
00:01:17,670 --> 00:01:19,560
Then I won't drink
the soup of forgetfulness.

29
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:21,870
Even if we're separated
by thousands of miles,

30
00:01:22,110 --> 00:01:23,280
I'll find you.

31
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:26,280
What if I become

32
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,950
a rogue in the next life,

33
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:29,870
fleeing to the ends of the earth?

34
00:01:30,670 --> 00:01:32,110
You won't be able to chase me.

35
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:35,110
Then I'll become a constable.

36
00:01:35,870 --> 00:01:38,510
No matter where you flee,
I'll hunt you down.

37
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:41,750
You are speaking nonsense
before Bodhisattva.

38
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:43,200
You deserve a beating.

39
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:17,140
♪The lush and fragrant grass
made longing hard to endure♪

40
00:02:17,180 --> 00:02:20,700
♪Can I entrust my heart to you?♪

41
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:23,580
♪This love is hard to fade away
as it twists and turns endlessly♪

42
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:27,060
♪On the path of emotions♪

43
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:30,820
♪Reflected in a mirror
by moonlight through a window♪

44
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:33,860
♪How much is your affection?♪

45
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:40,020
♪When the time to love is not right,
worldly matters make it hard to endure♪

46
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:42,660
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

47
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:47,580
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea ♪

48
00:02:48,020 --> 00:02:53,340
♪I accompany you
for a part of the journey♪

49
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:55,940
♪Our longing for each other
guides us through countless lives♪

50
00:02:56,060 --> 00:03:01,060
♪The flowers of the entire city
blossom for a person♪

51
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:06,420
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

52
00:03:20,860 --> 00:03:24,020
♪My dream is rising
in my heart like a spiral♪

53
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:27,260
♪The fate of our meeting
has been decided♪

54
00:03:27,380 --> 00:03:30,260
♪Your smile under the lantern♪

55
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:33,740
♪Stirs up my thoughts like crazy♪

56
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:37,540
♪The moonlight is dancing
and the fireflies are twinkling♪

57
00:03:37,740 --> 00:03:40,620
♪No one knows
how deep my love is for you♪

58
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:46,780
♪When you respond,
all is well in this world♪

59
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:53,160
This place is so beautiful.

60
00:03:57,390 --> 00:03:58,880
Do you have any other wishes?

61
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:01,710
The thing I want most

62
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:03,920
is already in my arms.

63
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,710
You miss Fu Bao, don't you?

64
00:04:10,270 --> 00:04:11,760
He's arriving tomorrow morning.

65
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:14,350
How do you know what's on my mind?

66
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:17,400
My eyes have never left you.

67
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,750
I know everything

68
00:04:19,190 --> 00:04:20,400
that's in your heart.

69
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,670
I never imagined

70
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:27,770
we could be so happy like this.

71
00:04:28,990 --> 00:04:30,240
Up until now,

72
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,280
it all feels like a dream.

73
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:33,630
Silly,

74
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,040
I'm right here in front of you.

75
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,040
You're by my side too.

76
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,550
From now on,

77
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:43,630
every day will be a good day.

78
00:04:44,750 --> 00:04:46,670
You'll focus on being a good city lord,

79
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:51,040
and I'll take care of our family
and raise the children.

80
00:04:51,670 --> 00:04:54,360
I don't seek glory or fame,

81
00:04:55,110 --> 00:04:57,110
just the happiness
and health of our family.

82
00:04:57,110 --> 00:05:00,230
And we can be together forever.

83
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,310
All right, I promise you.

84
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,600
I'll listen to you in everything.

85
00:05:07,180 --> 00:05:11,100
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

86
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:13,990
By the way,

87
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:16,550
when Fu Bao comes here,

88
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:18,230
there's something I want to tell you.

89
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,630
Don't worry,

90
00:05:20,430 --> 00:05:22,310
I'll get along with Fu Bao just fine.

91
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,110
It's not about that.

92
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:25,400
Do you

93
00:05:26,110 --> 00:05:27,280
have any secrets?

94
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,600
Tell me now.

95
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:35,220
♪Aren't the characters
in the play you and me?♪

96
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,680
My Lady,

97
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,720
His Lordship has gone out
to pick up the young master.

98
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,950
He specifically asked me

99
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,560
to tell you to rest a little longer.

100
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,750
I'm well-rested.

101
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,670
Once the rain stops,

102
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,320
I'll go to the gate to greet them.

103
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,240
Yes, My Lady.

104
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:51,660
[City Lord's Mansion]

105
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,270
I've been asked
to deliver a letter to you.

106
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:10,500
[To Su Wan'er]

107
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,240
Fu Bao.

108
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,630
Today is the first day

109
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,840
of our family of three being together.

110
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,630
We should celebrate properly.

111
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,360
I bought your favorite pastries

112
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,750
from Qinghe Restaurant.

113
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,150
By the way,

114
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:20,720
Ling Xiao,

115
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:23,150
I heard some rumors today.

116
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,670
What rumors?

117
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:27,840
I heard that there's
something mysterious in the world

118
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:29,600
that can control people's minds.

119
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,120
Without lifting a finger,

120
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,870
it can make others commit suicide.

121
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:37,120
You're knowledgeable,

122
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,670
do you know what this thing is?

123
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:44,760
Such nonsense rumors,

124
00:10:45,310 --> 00:10:46,310
only you would believe in them.

125
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,280
I received this today.

126
00:10:55,540 --> 00:10:56,100
[To Su Wan'er]

127
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:11,880
What's wrong?

128
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,430
Niyue is still the same.

129
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:18,000
Cunning and sowing discord.

130
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,120
Let's not let her

131
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:22,040
ruin our mood today.

132
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,710
Come, try this.

133
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:05,620
♪People sit silently
by candlelight as night begins♪

134
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:11,500
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

135
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:16,780
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

136
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:18,460
♪Everyone is filled
with sorrow and pity♪

137
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:22,340
♪Alas, the mortal world
has too many spectators♪

138
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:29,460
♪You turn back to ascend
the stage wearing a green robe♪

139
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:35,220
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

140
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:41,020
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

141
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,500
♪You sing for me♪

142
00:12:42,620 --> 00:12:46,420
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

143
00:12:46,660 --> 00:12:52,460
♪Pear blossoms fall
and flowing sleeves feel like yesterday♪

144
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:58,620
♪The heart is closed,
unable to gaze at the emotional eyes♪

145
00:12:58,660 --> 00:13:01,580
♪This life is filled
with too much affection♪

146
00:13:01,740 --> 00:13:05,260
♪Amid the applause,
who can see through it?♪
